{
 "cells": [

   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "737e6086-5638-4e74-b26f-845adc4dfffc",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Document and Page methods\n",
    "\n",
    "This example covers the use of some methods in the `Document` and `Page` class. All methods in the `Document` class are also available at the `Page` level. `Page` is an entity of the `Document`."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e251f5b2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Installation\n",
    "\n",
    "To begin, install the `amazon-textract-textractor` package using pip.\n",
    "\n",
    "`pip install amazon-textract-textractor`\n",
    "\n",
    "There are various sets of dependencies available to tailor your installation to your use case. The base package will have sensible default, but you may want to install the PDF extra dependencies if you workflow uses PDFs with `pip install amazon-textract-textractor[pdf]`. You can read more on extra dependencies [in the documentation](https://aws-samples.github.io/amazon-textract-textractor/installation.html)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "84de4512-2b2e-4d1d-9199-c9a483006df3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Calling Textract"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "fa86d86f-6272-4021-b4da-aa751ae2e22e",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "from PIL import Image\n",
    "from textractor import Textractor\n",
    "from textractor.visualizers.entitylist import EntityList\n",
    "from textractor.data.constants import TextractFeatures, Direction, DirectionalFinderType\n",
    "\n",
    "extractor = Textractor(aws_profile_name='default')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7d2ab9b8-1fff-4181-a035-84975111cbe0",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Input Document\n",
    "\n",
    "Here's a look at the document we wish to run Textractor on."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "ddf2a9e6-f47e-423e-ad3e-5e80f1fa4ee7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.PngImagePlugin.PngImageFile image mode=RGBA size=612x792>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 8,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "image = Image.open(\"../../../tests/fixtures/acord_form_2_05272022.png\")\n",
    "image"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "3f302ac5-02c9-4193-aa64-182a54c44dd0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "document = extractor.analyze_document(\n",
    "    file_source=image,\n",
    "    features=[TextractFeatures.TABLES, TextractFeatures.FORMS], \n",
    "    save_image=True\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "808c93c6-ba7f-43ae-929f-33b97b8ea630",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Numpy Indexing on Tables"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b44d9f71-d05e-4fae-bdc9-d8c73267fea5",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Retrieval of all tables in the document\n",
    "Table data is stored at the document and page level as a property and can be accessed as shown below."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "d65a0edc-58e8-4dbd-a8f6-4883c5859c94",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# All tables present in the document\n",
    "tables = document.tables"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "19a40312-1784-41ed-9e9c-5cb718960748",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Choose desired table among all the document tables"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "3b49c840-8b42-4292-a1d7-5607a1a3b667",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Choose specific table\n",
    "chosen_table = tables[1]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "id": "b2549d4b-bfa6-4356-88a6-4176aec260fb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGBA size=577x230>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 11,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "bbox = chosen_table.bbox\n",
    "image.crop((\n",
    "    bbox.x * image.width,\n",
    "    bbox.y * image.height,\n",
    "    (bbox.x + bbox.width) * image.width,\n",
    "    (bbox.y + bbox.height) * image.height,\n",
    "))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "4a5a816f-d92e-45dc-b0e9-2f7c06b068ef",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Filter and display table \n",
    "\n",
    "To make the interface of accessing 2D data intuitive, the table filtering supports numpy indexing. Finally, to print the table contents in a structured manner, the `pretty_print()` method from EntityList class can be called upon it. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 21,
   "id": "9eb9039d-76ae-4cc9-a527-f57a1aad29e5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "|------------------------------------------------------------------|----------------|-----------------|\n",
      "| NAME AND LOCATION OF AND ALL COMPANIES (Demente Operations)      | ANNUAL PAYHOLL | ANN CHOSS SALES |\n",
      "| Gary 4002 Oficul Dogwood K. Garrison Road Phoenix, AZ 85012      | 90             | 90              |\n",
      "| Hire 3640 Jessie Melvile D. Fox Street Jackson, TN 38301         | 24             | 95              |\n",
      "| Loabing 2289 Roberta Thompaon K. Sykes Street Whillier, CA 90802 | 24             | 67              |\n",
      "| 2573 Jo Kanbving Stark Temple Hollow Hoad Mesiter, co 81841      | 32             | 84              |\n",
      "| 2534 Holeking Doug P. Brown Read PA 15319                        | 98             | 78              |\n",
      "| 4461 Karen Jessing Mesa T. Clay Drive Las Vegas, NV 89101        | 88             | 46              |\n",
      "\n",
      "\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "filtered_table = chosen_table[:, 2:5]\n",
    "table_string = EntityList(filtered_table).pretty_print()\n",
    "print(table_string)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "1c710fd4-824b-40f9-9308-774fd0ab691b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Retrieving key-values and checkboxes by geometry using directional_finder()\n",
    "\n",
    "It is possible to retrieve key-values and checkboxes present in a certain location of the document using reference words and direction of the required key-values and checkboxes with respect to them."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 22,
   "id": "e85b4458-671b-4770-b8e3-5a01f5e2617c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "page = document.page(0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 23,
   "id": "b6c8abca-30f0-4753-854e-738e4da81fe6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "[RETHDACTIVE DATE FOR EBL : 07/18/2020,\n",
       " LIVII OF INSURANCE (Ex Employee : 1600.00,\n",
       " NAME OF BENEMI PROCHAM : Innovation,\n",
       " LIMII FOREBL : 1850.00,\n",
       " ACCIECAIE LIMII FOREBL : 1900.00]"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 23,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "page.directional_finder(\n",
    "    word_1=\"employee benefits and liability\",\n",
    "    word_2=\"primary location and subsidiaries\",\n",
    "    prefix =\"\", \n",
    "    direction=Direction.BELOW,\n",
    "    entities=[DirectionalFinderType.KEY_VALUE_SET],\n",
    "    edit_original=False\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5a2de684-5533-4cbf-bec7-4724bd96609f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Visualize results"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 24,
   "id": "9e5cfb1d-af5b-4f43-a506-4f503ad9760b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=612x792>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 24,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "key_value_result = page.directional_finder(\n",
    "    word_1=\"employee benefits and liability\",\n",
    "    word_2=\"primary location and subsidiaries\",\n",
    "    prefix =\"\", \n",
    "    direction=Direction.BELOW,\n",
    "    entities=[DirectionalFinderType.KEY_VALUE_SET],\n",
    "    edit_original=False\n",
    ")\n",
    "key_value_result.visualize()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 25,
   "id": "2bde4cfb-1490-4c0a-8ab5-efd84717c3fc",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "[[X] MENEWAL,\n",
       " [X] VOLUNTARY,\n",
       " [ ] HISS DEFENSE DOLLAR (Y N),\n",
       " [X] NEW,\n",
       " [X] Excess,\n",
       " [X] OCCUMHENCE,\n",
       " [X] CLAIMS MADE,\n",
       " [X] UMBRELLA]"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 25,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "page.directional_finder(\n",
    "    word_1=\"policy information\",\n",
    "    word_2=\"employee benefits and liability\",\n",
    "    direction=Direction.BELOW,\n",
    "    entities=[DirectionalFinderType.SELECTION_ELEMENT],\n",
    "    edit_original=False\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 26,
   "id": "111ab6f1-a72c-4bc6-8510-1a7be8ada5da",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<PIL.Image.Image image mode=RGB size=612x792>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 26,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "selection_element_result = page.directional_finder(\n",
    "    word_1=\"policy information\",\n",
    "    word_2=\"employee benefits and liability\",\n",
    "    direction=Direction.BELOW,\n",
    "    entities=[DirectionalFinderType.SELECTION_ELEMENT],\n",
    "    edit_original=False\n",
    ")\n",
    "selection_element_result.visualize()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "71d1c33c-213a-4131-a1a0-e0f01f61a09b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Identifing duplication in key-values and table data\n",
    "\n",
    "Some time the key and values extracted from a document will also be part of a table, causing information duplication. This example will go over identifying such duplicated information."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 27,
   "id": "eb741dd0-d4de-4350-b03b-db315967e46c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "duplicates = page.return_duplicates()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0814f135-230f-45a6-b207-92ad02b485bd",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
